        "# 🏥 NexusHealth — Weekly PySpark ETL & ML Retraining\n",
        "\n",
        "This notebook runs the **PySpark ETL, Delta Lake transformations, and ML model retraining** entirely in the cloud for free using Google Colab's hosted servers (no local system resources used).\n",
        "\n",
        "[![Open In Colab](https://colab.research.google.com/assets/colab-badge.svg)](https://colab.research.google.com/github/stevegonsalves18/NexusHealth/blob/main/docs/Healthcare_Retraining_Colab.ipynb)"
      ]
    },
